title: Knife Fight S04E01 Jamon Iberico WS.DSR.x264-[NY2].mp4
description:
Knife Fight - Season 4, Episode 1




Round 1: Jamon Iberico

Brooklyn's own Jason Marcus takes on the boundless energy and bold style of Top Chef finalist Angelo Sosa. In this season 4 premiere, it's all about Jamon Iberico. To advance in the tournament, the chefs must impress our judges: James Beard winner Sue Zemanick and Dale Talde, head of the Talde restaurant empire. It's go big or go home for the chefs in this first round match up.




Original Air Date: 10-Nov-2015
